OL,3,CPadiham Pool stars in new indie film
OL,4,C'The Baths'
OL,6,FWhat do you do if you want to get your
OL,7,Fvery own film idea commissioned?
OL,9,FWell.. do it yourself! That's the
OL,10,Fmessage from one based aspiring film
OL,11,Fmaker.
OL,13,FJack Hartley from had an idea about a
OL,14,Ffilm set in a local swimming baths so
OL,15,Finstead of talking about it - he went
OL,16,Fout there and did it.
