OL,3,CPadiham Pool stars in new indie film
OL,4,C'The Baths'
OL,6,FJack says: "The story follows the
OL,7,Fcomplexities between the staff and the
OL,8,Fmembers and the day-to-day running of
OL,9,Fa fictional swimming baths in the
OL,10,Ffictional northern town of Gorple.
OL,12,F"I never even approached any funding
OL,13,Fbodies- I reached out to a couple of
OL,14,Flocal people that I thought could be
OL,15,Fsuitable for those characters so we
OL,16,Fgot a small crew together and came and
OL,17,Fdid it!"
OL,19,FThe film is called The Baths, and
OL,20,Fstars Shameless and Benidorm star
OL,21,FAlice Barry.
