OL,4,C'The Baths'
OL,6,FThe actress didn't have far to travel
OL,7,Fto work, as she lives in Padiham too.
OL,9,FShe said: "Oh, loved it. Loved it.
OL,10,FAnything local I love, you know, and
OL,11,FI'm really enjoying this part, you
OL,12,Fknow, because I play Janice who is the
OL,13,Fmanageress of the pool.
OL,15,F"People always stop me and say, oh you
OL,16,Fwere in Benidorm and in Shameless. My
OL,17,Fgrandson lives in Padiham, and when he
OL,18,Fwas out in Iraq they had shameless on
OL,19,Fand they used to shout to him Hey,
OL,20,Fyour grandmas on!"
