OL,6,FThe film is yet to be released in it's
OL,7,Fentirety, but snippets have been
OL,8,Freleased on reels and clips on social
OL,9,Fmedia.
OL,11,F"Eventually, down the line, we will
OL,12,Frelease it to the public. I can
OL,13,Fdefinitely see it as a six part
OL,14,Fseries. It's all about them. It's not
OL,15,Fjust about me" says JackJ"It's about
OL,16,Feveryone. In the community"
